snippet.title: Coins - A Coin collecting game Trailer
snippet.description:
Coins is a Free To Play Idler Clicker Coin collecting game coming this August to Steam

You can get, collect and trade Coins by just playing the game, you only need a Steam account and you will be ready to go!

Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3083090/Coins/
